{
  "version": 1,
  "lines": {
    "load": ["欢迎来到 GWB Wiki。", "今天也适合抬头看云。"],
    "relax": ["我在这里看云。", "这片海和天空的边界有点模糊。"],
    "click": ["我在听。", "需要搜索资料的话，可以点上面的搜索框。", "别点太急，云也要慢慢看。"],
    "error": ["看板娘资源暂时没有加载成功。"]
  },
  "rules": [
    {
      "event": "load",
      "text": ["欢迎来到 GWB Wiki。", "今天也适合抬头看云。"],
      "cooldownMs": 12000
    },
    {
      "selector": ".md-logo, .md-header__title",
      "event": "mouseenter",
      "text": ["回到首页的话，从这里走。", "GWB Wiki，正在漂浮。"],
      "cooldownMs": 8000
    },
    {
      "selector": ".md-search",
      "event": "mouseenter",
      "text": ["想找哪一种云？输入关键词试试。", "搜索框已经待命。"],
      "action": "touch",
      "cooldownMs": 8000
    },
    {
      "selector": ".md-search__input",
      "event": "focus",
      "text": ["我会帮你盯着搜索结果。", "关键词越准，云层越清楚。"],
      "action": "touch",
      "cooldownMs": 7000
    },
    {
      "selector": ".home-search",
      "event": "mouseenter",
      "text": ["这里可以搜索整个 Wiki。", "找不到的时候，先从这里开始。"],
      "action": "touch",
      "cooldownMs": 7000
    },
    {
      "selector": ".home-random",
      "event": "mouseenter",
      "text": ["随机云图，适合抽一朵今天的云。", "要不要看看下一片天空？"],
      "action": "special",
      "cooldownMs": 7000
    },
    {
      "selector": ".home-links a[href*='china-cloud-atlas']",
      "event": "mouseenter",
      "text": ["中国云图清单，像一本天空索引。", "这里适合认真翻资料。"],
      "cooldownMs": 7000
    },
    {
      "selector": ".home-links a:not(.home-random)",
      "event": "mouseenter",
      "text": ["这是一条快速入口。", "这边也能过去。"],
      "cooldownMs": 7000
    },
    {
      "selector": ".home-card[href='clouds/']",
      "event": "mouseenter",
      "text": ["进入云的图谱。", "卷云、积云、层云，都在里面。"],
      "action": "touch",
      "cooldownMs": 8000
    },
    {
      "selector": ".home-card[href='jellyfish/']",
      "event": "mouseenter",
      "text": ["进入水母花园。", "这边是海里的云。"],
      "action": "touch",
      "cooldownMs": 8000
    },
    {
      "selector": ".md-source",
      "event": "mouseenter",
      "text": ["这里可以去 GitHub 看源码。", "代码也会留下云的轨迹。"],
      "cooldownMs": 10000
    },
    {
      "selector": ".md-header__button[for^='__palette']",
      "event": "mouseenter",
      "text": ["白天和夜晚，云的样子会变。"],
      "cooldownMs": 15000
    }
  ]
}
